    "365:28": "śrīmato'nāthanāthasya gṛhasthasya mahāmateḥ|",
    "365:29": "vihāre jetakodhyāne vijahāra sasāṃghikaḥ||",
    "365:30": "tadā tatra mahāsattvā bodhiosattvā jinātmajāḥ|",
