    "365:76": "sainyā yodhṛgaṇāścāpi bhṛtyāḥ parijanā api|",
    "365:77": "gṛhasthā dhaninaḥ sārthavāhādayo vaṇiggaṇāḥ||",
    "365:78": "śilpinaṃ kṝṣiṇaścāpi sarve kuṭumbino'pi ca|",
