    "365:86": "taṃ munīndraṃ samālokya praṇamantaḥ purogatāḥ||",
    "365:87": "yathāvidhi samabhyarcya praṇatvā ca yathākramam|",
    "365:88": "tistraḥ pradakṣiṇīkṛtya kṛtāṃjalipuṭā mudā||",
    "365:89": "tatsaddharmāmṛtaṃ pātuṃ parivṛtya samantataḥ|",
    "365:90": "puraskṛtya samādhāya paśyantaḥ samupāśrayan||",
