    "365:95": "tadā tadraśmisaṃspṛṣṭe vihāre tatra sarvataḥ|",
    "365:96": "hemaratnamayā āsan stambhāḥ sarve praśobhitāḥ||",
    "365:97": "kūṭāgārāśca sarve'pi suvarṇaratnaśobhitāḥ|",
    "365:98": "dvārāṇi tatra sarvāṇi hemarupyamayāni ca||",
    "365:99": "sopānānyapi sarvāṇi svarṇarupyamayāni ca|",
    "365:100": "vātāyanāni sarvāṇi hemaratnamayāni ca||",
